Item Management System
This project is a web-based item management system that allows users to Create, Read, Update, and Delete items. It utilizes jQuery and AJAX for client-side interactions and connects to a server-side API for data operations.

Technologies Used
    Front-end: HTML, CSS, jQuery
    Back-end: Node.js, Express.js
    Database: MongoDB

Setup
    *Modify for your MongoDB 
        const connectionString = 'mongodb://localhost:27017/mydatabase'; // Replace with your database connection string

    *Make Collection of Persons Data
        Sample data
        [
            {
                "_id": "64f9c31b9d3f5c4b8d4e9a1a",
                "name": "Vivaan Gupta",
                "email": "vivaan.gupta@example.com",
                "contact": "1234567890"
            },
            {
                "_id": "64f9c31b9d3f5c4b8d4e9a1b",
